&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户现在可以将Windows PC的整个桌面或任意单个应用窗口，以无线、低延迟的方式无缝“拉入”头显</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的无线虚拟屏幕之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">用户可以在一个完全沉浸、不受物理边界限制的环境中使用Photoshop、CAD等专业软件进行创作，也开启了全新的娱乐方式——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将高性能PC游戏串流至头显</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其次，为了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">解决用户在佩戴头显进行视频通话时“隐身”的社交尴尬</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，谷歌推出了Likeness功能。这项技术允许用户创建一个高度逼真的个人数字人化身。该化身并非静态模型，而是能够通过头显的传感器实时、精确地镜像用户的所有面部微妙表情、口型动作乃至头部的自然转动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078572\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"426\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.775 / 1;\" data-backw=\"426\" data-backh=\"240\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=539f38d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fow6przZuPIEW8gMMI1qtBBMvXQcRdfShT0cteuY12CLgiaUicKic8qnNctLxosadMXBceYwTickQ6l5EhicG7Wnbichg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在Google Meet等视频会议中，与会者看到的将是一个栩栩如生、表情同步的“你”，极大地增强了虚拟社交的真实感与临场感，让远程协作和沟通变得更为自然亲切。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第三，为了拓展头显的使用场景至移动环境，全新的Travel Mode应运而生，利用先进的算法智能补偿外部运动带来的干扰，显著稳定用户视野中的虚拟画面，减少因画面抖动而产生的眩晕感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078573\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"426\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.775 / 1;\" data-backw=\"426\" data-backh=\"240\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d35e8f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fow6przZuPIEW8gMMI1qtBBMvXQcRdfShIqLCW88iadhWic3x95vwE5Qcku5E8bKx4KzulNw1gYPHAQbYX7kK1WwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除了上述即刻可用的三大功能，谷歌还预告了一项计划于明年推出的核心技术——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">系统级自动空间化，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在系统底层，实时、自动地将任何普通的2D应用界面，动态转化为具有立体深度和空间感的3D沉浸式体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此举将无需开发者进行单独适配，从而有望瞬间极大地丰富XR生态的内容库，将整个数字世界“空间化”，预示着沉浸式交互将从特定应用走向普适化体验的未来。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><strong><mark style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"></mark><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">04 开发工具包更新</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">面向开发者社区，谷歌同步发布了Android XR SDK开发者预览版3（DP3）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本次更新的核心在于首次正式开放了对AI智能眼镜的完整开发支持，标志着Android XR平台从沉浸式头显正式延伸至全天候佩戴的智能可穿戴领域。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078570\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5916666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.69129 / 1;\" data-backw=\"554\" data-backh=\"328\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ce8954a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIEW8gMMI1qtBBMvXQcRdfShyKzZBFAzBEXeKGArr3RBuRMHwL6qY4sHEKQ3x80PwyLk4IOK0vpcUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为帮助开发者高效构建面向未来的眼镜应用，谷歌推出了两大专属开发库：&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Jetpack Glimmer是一个专为透明显示屏设计的现代化UI工具包，基于Compose构建，它提供了经过精心优化、符合眼镜交互逻辑的界面组件（如卡片、列表），让开发者能够轻松创建清晰、优雅且对现实世界干扰最小的视觉体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Jetpack Projected则是一个基础API库，它旨在解决生态扩展的初始挑战，允许开发者将现有Android手机应用的核心功能与业务逻辑，通过简洁的接口快速“投射”至眼镜平台，管理音频与摄像头访问，从而实现从移动端到眼镜端的平滑过渡，显著简化了开发流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在增强现实能力方面，SDK集成了ARCore for Jetpack XR，并新增了关键的地理空间API。这使得开发者能够利用全球规模的视觉定位服务，构建出基于精确地理位置与现实场景识别的应用，例如提供实时的AR步行导航。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了构建一个开放且充满活力的生态，Android XR遵循OpenXR这一行业开放标准。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在游戏与高沉浸感内容创作领域，Unreal Engine现已能够利用其原生OpenXR支持为Android XR进行开发。谷歌还宣布，其官方提供的专属插件（将集成更深度的手部追踪等平台特性）预计于2026年初发布，以进一步释放引擎的创作潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与此同时，开源的Godot引擎已在其v4.2.2稳定版中，通过官方插件提供了对Android XR的完整支持，为独立开发者和小型团队提供了强大而灵活的选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一个生动的开发者案例来自Uber，他们演示了如何利用新工具为带显示屏的AI智能眼镜重塑出行体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当乘客抵达机场，眼镜的透明显示屏上会浮现出行程状态与预计到达时间，让信息获取无需低头。通过集成的AR路径引导，虚拟箭头会清晰地叠加在真实的航站楼环境中，引导用户步行至准确的上车点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"544078574\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5864583333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;border:0px none;width:100%;max-width:100%;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;aspect-ratio:1.70479 / 1;\" data-backw=\"554\" data-backh=\"325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=57d4467d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fow6przZuPIEW8gMMI1qtBBMvXQcRdfSh6s61VHslPPeNT9LVcv2RiaHpQyUBjSb8SIXLniciaTQKmibicbIlxOy4ERA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终，车辆信息（如车牌号）会直接显示在视野中，用户甚至可通过眼镜便捷地呼叫司机，整个过程实现了信息与物理世界的无缝融合，让用户始终保持抬头、解放双手。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">（</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">文/腾讯科技特约编译金鹿，编辑/苏扬</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">）</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌正式发布 Android XR 平台，联合三星、高通推出 AI 智能眼镜、有线 XR 眼镜及 Galaxy XR 头显，旨在统一 XR 生态并打造软硬件一体的沉浸式体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌正式发布 Android XR 平台，联合三星、高通推出 AI 智能眼镜、有线 XR 眼镜及 Galaxy XR 头显，旨在统一 XR 生态并打造软硬件一体的沉浸式体验。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了谷歌在 XR 领域的重要布局——Android XR 平台。该平台旨在将 Android 手机时代的优势延伸至 XR 设备，并与三星、高通合作打造\"亲儿子\"系列产品，包括时尚的 AI 智能眼镜（含屏幕和无屏幕版本，2026 年推出）以及和 XREAL 合作的有线 XR 眼镜 Project Aura。此外，三星的 Galaxy XR 头显也基于此平台升级了 PC Connect、Likeness 和 Travel Mode 等功能，并预告了系统级自动空间化技术。文章还强调了 Android XR SDK 开发者工具包的更新，为 AI 智能眼镜提供开发支持，并通过 Jetpack Glimmer、Jetpack Projected、ARCore for Jetpack XR 等工具简化开发，并宣布支持 OpenXR 标准，兼容 Unreal Engine 和 Godot 引擎，展示了 Uber 的 AR 导航应用案例，全面勾勒出谷歌构建统一、开放 XR 生态的愿景。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "谷歌 Android XR 平台旨在整合 XR 设备生态。",
      "explanation": "Android XR 作为\"业界首个为扩展现实设备打造的统一平台\"，计划将 Android 在智能手机领域的成功复制到 XR，提供一致的用户和开发体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "谷歌与合作伙伴共同推出多元化 XR 硬件。",
      "explanation": "谷歌联手三星、高通以及 Warby Parker、Gentle Monster、XREAL 等品牌，推出 AI 智能眼镜、有线 XR 眼镜 Project Aura 和 Galaxy XR 头显，覆盖不同形态和应用场景的 XR 设备。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 能力深度赋能 XR 设备体验。",
      "explanation": "AI 智能眼镜通过 Gemini AI 提供情境感知、视觉搜索、实时翻译、多模态 AI 创作等功能；Galaxy XR 头显的 Likeness 功能通过 AI 生成逼真数字人，提升虚拟社交真实感。"
    },
    {
      "point": "开发者工具包更新，降低 XR 开发门槛。",
      "explanation": "Android XR SDK DP3 开放了 AI 智能眼镜开发支持，并推出 Jetpack Glimmer、Jetpack Projected 等工具，集成 ARCore for Jetpack XR，并支持 OpenXR、Unreal Engine 和 Godot 引擎，助力开发者快速构建应用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "系统级自动空间化技术将重塑 XR 内容生态。",
      "explanation": "谷歌预告的系统级自动空间化技术，能将 2D 应用自动转化为 3D 沉浸式体验，有望极大丰富 XR 内容，实现沉浸式交互的普适化，意义深远。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "谷歌将 Android XR 定位为\"业界首个为扩展现实设备打造的统一平台\"。",
    "Android XR 的设计哲学，是将扩展现实视为一个连续的设备谱系，而非单一产品形态，翻译过来就是，产品形态很多元。",
    "产品体验则完全围绕 Gemini AI 构建，致力于提供一种\"情境感知式\"的无感协助。",
